data.description: Welcome to your future home! This fantastic 5-bed, 4-bath residence in the sought-after Breckenridge Forest North neighborhood is ready to become your family's haven. With a spacious 3-car attached garage, a charming fenced backyard, open game room, media room, and an oversized extra/flex room to "die for"!!! This remarkable property is equipped with a water softener system and GENERAC generator service. Schedule a showing today and start creating cherished memories by making this beautiful home yours.
